<P>
HEARSE INJURES MOURNERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A hired funeral car plowed into a group of 100 mourners, seriously injuring 
two, after the driver accidentally knocked the automatic gearshift, Japanese 
police said Friday. They said the 64-year-old limousine driver was arrested and 
charged with negligence. 
</P>
