<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032694-0123 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 026415 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 26, 1994, Saturday, Southland Edition 
</P>
