</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
56 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Improv info -- Jennifer Coolidge is the Groundlings performer in the 
photograph that ran on page 1 of Friday's Calendar. She was misidentified in 
the caption. In the related story on Los Angeles improv, the wrong day was 
listed for QBalls Improv Comedy -- the group performs Saturdays at 8 p.m. at 
QBalls Billiard Club in Pasadena. 
</P>
</TEXT>
